      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut </strong>in 350ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[450ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p>",
