    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Strip your <strong>coriander leaves </strong>from their stalks and chop the stalks finely (save the leaves for garnish!)</p><p>Slice your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> finely into strips</p><p>Tip: Not a fan of spice? Remove the seeds!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/857.-step-4-x200.jpg",
